@DATABASE "Project Future"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - P - Project Future"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - P
                   ====================================

                              Project Future
                              ==============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"No Enemies" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(27662,0)"}              27662,0
@{"Lives = x " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(30147,255)"}              30147,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

@endnode
